式出道之前，该组合的四位成员已经发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-of-life-belle-julie-countdown-kitty-cat-music-video-release-3458690">独奏曲目</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-of-life-natty-solo-sugarcoat-music-video-release-3457824">音乐视频</a>，这些视频后来被收录在他们的首张迷你专辑中。该项目还收录了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-of-life-music-video-for-b-side-bye-my-neverland-3462348">B 面曲目“Bye My Neverland”</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-of-life-julie-n-word-apology-past-use-pre-debut-performance-3472293">《KISS OF LIFE》的朱莉为过去在首演前的表演中使用“N”字而道歉的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
