e and became a member of the project girl group <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/i.o.i">IOI</a> .</p><p> In other K-pop news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newjeans">NewJeans</a> recently dropped a music video for &#39;ETA&#39;, a song from their new sophomore mini-album &#39;Get Up&#39;. The record also features the previously released songs <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-super-shy-3464950">&#39;Super Shy&#39;</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jung-ho-yeon-tony-leung-newjeans-cool-with-you-music-video-3470889">&#39;Cool With You&#39;</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-transform-into-the-powerpuff-girls-in-new-jeans-mv-3465954">&#39;New Jeans&#39;</a> , among others.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeon-somi-ep-game-plan-3472285">Jeon Somi announces new EP &#39;Game Plan&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
